law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 428, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1982. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 386, sec. 102. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1379-8.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Capias pro fine -- Persons arrested on may be delivered to workhouse.
